title: Telemedicina 24H DoctorGO
description:
DoctorGO, The Doctor, Nutritionist and your Personal Trainer always with you.

 

With DoctorGO, the 100% digital Online Health APP, you will have Telemedicine with chat and Video Consultations 24 hours a day, with which you can resolve your medical questions in less than 2 minutes, at any time, every day of the year and with no limit on consultations. And now, at no additional cost, it includes video consultations of up to 30 minutes with a Psychologist.

 

Our coaches will also design Personalized Nutrition and Fitness Plans to get you in shape and improve your health. Additionally, you can train from anywhere.

Also, with DoctorGO you can receive electronic Prescriptions on your mobile phone and order your medications with free shipping thanks to the Telepharmacy service.

 

An App to take care of your family, with which you can invite a friend or family member for free and forever. So that you, your guest and all the children in the house are well taken care of.

 

Consult with a general practitioner or a specialist, always through your mobile. These are our 9 specialties:

-General medicine.

-Allergology.

-Cardiology.

-Dermatology.

-Gynecology.

-Pediatrics.

-Psychology.

-Sexology.

-Nutrition and diet.

-Personal trainer.

 

Try the DoctorGO app for free without obligation, and if you like it, start taking care of your family for only 10 euros/month and also because it is from Yoigo, €24/year discount on your telephone bill (Includes 2 adults + children by subscription)
